[
  {
    "speaker": "char_wang_da_yan",
    "speaker_name": "王大眼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "这是我送给我老婆的，怎么会到你手里了？你最好快一点给我从实招来。",
    "tone": "质问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wang_da_yan",
    "speaker_name": "王大眼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "这是我花了整整三两银子买来的。",
    "tone": "供述",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_wang_da_yan",
    "text": "谁卖给你的？",
    "tone": "追问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wang_da_yan",
    "speaker_name": "王大眼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "除了那个小王八蛋之外还有谁？",
    "tone": "愤恨",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wang_da_yan",
    "speaker_name": "王大眼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "平常这个小王八蛋穷得要死，可是柳大爷一死，他就阔了，我一直怀疑他见财起意，谋财害命。",
    "tone": "怀疑",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_wang_da_yan",
    "speaker_name": "王大眼",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "这个小王八蛋平常窝在些什么地方，没有人比我更清楚，我准能把他找到。",
    "tone": "自信",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": null,
    "text": "好快的刀。",
    "tone": "感叹",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我知道你一定会替我担心，我自己却一点都不担心，因为我自己一直觉得宫素素不能把我怎么样。",
    "tone": "感慨",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "我连作梦都没有想到许老太能一下子就把我制住。",
    "tone": "惊讶",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "许老太是谁？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "就是那天替你开门的老婆婆。",
    "tone": "解释",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "你有没有看见那个小叫化？",
    "tone": "追问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "可是我从来也没有想到他会是这么样一个人，居然会冒险来救我。",
    "tone": "感动",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "他是不是已经遭了毒手？",
    "tone": "担忧",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "就算他现在还活着，恐怕也活不长久。",
    "tone": "黯然",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "为什么？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "因为他好像知道一件绝不愿意让别人知道的秘密。",
    "tone": "神秘",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "他好像还看到了一件他不该看到的事。",
    "tone": "神秘",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "现在这个小叫化的人在哪里？",
    "tone": "追问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "他已经被押走了，被宫素素和许老太押走的。",
    "tone": "告知",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "她们为什么要把他押走？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "如果她们要杀他灭口，为什么不索性就在这里杀了他？",
    "tone": "疑问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "如果你要杀一个人，你愿不愿意要他死在你自己家里？",
    "tone": "反问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "我不愿意。",
    "tone": "回答",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_gong_ping",
    "speaker_name": "宫萍",
    "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "text": "要一个人自己走到别的地方去死，是不是要比把一个死人搬出去容易得多？",
    "tone": "反问",
    "chapter": 9
  },
  {
    "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
    "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
    "listener": "char_gong_ping",
    "text": "是的。",
    "tone": "回答",
    "chapter": 9
  }
]